					<div class="item-page ">
 
 








<p><span style="color: #808080;"><strong><span style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 14pt;"><span class="s5">Villa&nbsp;</span><span class="s5">Adonia</span><span class="s5">&nbsp;and Villa Harmony - &nbsp;</span><span class="s5">Peyia,&nbsp;</span><span class="s5">Paphos</span><span class="s5">, Cyprus</span></span></strong></span></p>
<p><span class="s5" style="font-weight: bold; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;">Two neighbouring Luxury villas for holiday rent - both with separate Private pools and Gardens</span></p>
<p class="s6" style="margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: -webkit-auto;"><span class="s5" style="font-weight: bold; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;">These are available to rental, either singly, or together</span></p>
<p class="s4" style="margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 10px;"><span style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 14pt; color: #808080;"><span class="s5" style="font-weight: bold;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Adonia</span><span class="s5" style="font-weight: bold;">, 4 bed, sleeps 8</span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #808080;"><strong><span style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 14pt;"><span class="s5">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Harmony 3&nbsp;</span><span class="s5">bed,</span><span class="s5">&nbsp;sleeps 6</span></span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 8.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; color: #777777;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;">Situated on the sunny island of Cyprus - the jewel in the Mediterranean, with an average temperature of 24<span style="font-size: 5.7px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;"><sup>o</sup></span>C and almost 330 days of sunshine per year.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #808080;"></span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 8.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; color: #777777;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;">We are located in&nbsp;in the traditional Cypriot village of Peyia, overlooking Coral Bay and it's popular beach, in&nbsp;the Paphos area on the West of the island.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #808080;">&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12pt;">Our villas are conveniently located only 30 minutes from the Airport, 15 minutes from Paphos town and 5 minutes from Coral Bay. Both villas have stunning panoramic views of the coast and mountains, being two of the best available in this area.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #808080;">&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12pt;">The centre of Peyia village is within a 5 to 10 minute walk, where there are several bars,&nbsp;tavernas, take-aways, shops, banks, supermarkets and other amenities. Many guests rarely leave the villa and village<span style="line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">.</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #808080;">&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12pt;">Our 2 villas are neighbouring &nbsp;but each retaining privacy. With their own private landscaped gardens and spectacular Infinity Pool, both have panoramic sea and mountain views, which can be admired from both the pool area and the large balconies off the bedrooms, complete with separate outdoor furniture<span style="line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">.</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #808080;">&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12pt;">Both villas are light and airy. As they are built in traditional stone, each villa is cool in the summer&nbsp;and warmer in the winter.&nbsp;However air conditioning and central heating is available in each room at no extra cost.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #808080;">&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12pt;">Each villa has the following luxuries:</span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;"><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Air conditioning and central heating in every room</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;"><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Fire Place in each lounge (see each villa for details)</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;"><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Panoramic sea and&nbsp;mountain views</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;"><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Wi-Fi</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;"><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Internet TV with UK Free-view and access&nbsp;to global channels and sports</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;"><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Jacuzzi Bath</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;"><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Large Balconies</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;"><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Private parking</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;"><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space: pre;"> </span>Double-glazed windows</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 8.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; color: #777777;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;"><strong>Why choose us?</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li style="margin: 0px; font-size: 8.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; color: #777777;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;">&nbsp; &nbsp;Two of the best Villas in the Coral-Bay/Paphos area</span></li>
<li style="margin: 0px; font-size: 8.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; color: #777777;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;">&nbsp; &nbsp;Fantastic views, beautiful pools, privacy, great facilities...</span></li>
<li style="margin: 0px; font-size: 8.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; color: #777777;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;">&nbsp; &nbsp;Situated in a charming, traditional village, with great amenities</span></li>
<li style="margin: 0px; font-size: 8.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; color: #777777;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;">&nbsp; &nbsp;The owners have been renting these villas for 9 years - rent with confidence</span></li>
<li style="margin: 0px; font-size: 8.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; color: #777777;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;">&nbsp; &nbsp;We keep the villas in pristine condition, inside and out</span></li>
<li style="margin: 0px; font-size: 8.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; color: #777777;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;">&nbsp; &nbsp;The pools are infinity pools, that allow the views of the sea to add to the experience</span></li>
<li style="margin: 0px; font-size: 8.5px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; color: #777777;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #808080;">&nbsp; &nbsp;Read our reviews, guests agree that a holiday in our villas exceeds expectations</span></li>
</ul>
